Bridgit Claire Mendler (born December 18, 1992) is an American singer-songwriter, musician, producer and actress. She played Teddy Duncan in the Disney Channel Original Series Good Luck Charlie and appeared in the 2009 made for television film Labor Pains. In 2009, she became a recurring character for the Disney Channel Original Series Wizards of Waverly Place. In December of that year, she made her theatrical debut in the film Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakuel, released on December 23, 2009. Following the positive reception to her character on Wizards of Waverly Place, who was a vampire and fell in love with David Henrie's character, she became the star of the Disney series Good Luck Charlie, which premiered in April 2010 and ended in February 2014. In 2011, she appeared in the film based on the series Good Luck Charlie, It's Christmas.She starred in the Disney Channel Original Movie Lemonade Mouth, in which her character Olivia performs numerous songs. Two singles were released from the soundtrack featuring her vocals, with both charting on the US Billboard Hot 100. In 2012, Mendler released her debut album Hello My Name Is..., which featured a pop sound. It debuted at number 30 on the US Billboard 200, and has sold over 200,000 copies. Her debut single off the album "Ready or Not", became an international Top 40 hit, the song was certified gold in Norway, and platinum in New Zealand, United States and Canada and peaked at number 49 on the Billboard Hot 100. It was announced that her second single would be "Hurricane". The video premiered on April 12, 2013 and was shot in London. "Hurricane" has been certified gold in the USA for selling 500,000 copies.Mendler has links with several philanthropic projects and humanitarian causes. In 2010 Mendler became ambassador to First Book, a campaign to encourage reading and gives books to children in need. In July 2012 Bridgit also became ambassador of the campaign Give With Target with Target Corporation to raise funds to reform schools in the United States. Was featured in a March 2013 public campaign Delete Digital Drama with the Seventeen Magazine to end cyberbullying. In May 2013 Mendler traveled to the United Kingdom to fundraise for Comic Relief, given the aim of making her laugh with their jokes for a £1 donation. The campaign aimed to raising £100,000 and give families hope. In March, 2014 Mendler traveled to region of El Quiché, in Guatemala, to participate in the other project of Save the Children that helps underprivileged children in developing countries. Also represented the institution during the charity congress Save the Children's annual Advocacy Summit in Washington, D.C..

Bridgit Claire Mendler (n. 18 de diciembre de 1992) es una actriz, música y cantautora estadounidense. Interpretó a Teddy Duncan en la serie de Disney Channel ¡Buena Suerte, Charlie! luego apareció en la película hecha para televisión de 2009 Labor Pains. En 2009, Mendler se convirtió en un personaje recurrente de la serie de Disney Channel Wizards of Waverly Place. En diciembre de ese año, Mendler hizo su debut en cine en la película Alvin y las ardillas 2, estrenada el 23 de diciembre de 2009. Tras la buena acogida de su personaje en "Wizards", Mendler convirtió en la estrella de la serie de Disney ¡Buena Suerte, Charlie!, que se estrenó en abril de 2010. En 2011, Mendler apareció en la película Good Luck Charlie, It's Christmas!. Protagonizó la película Disney Channel Lemonade Mouth, en la que su personaje Olivia interpreta numerosas canciones. Dos sencillos fueron lanzados de la banda sonora con la voz de Mendler, ambos en la lista Billboard Hot 100. En 2012, Mendler lanzó su álbum debut Hello My Name Is..., que contó con un sonido pop. Debutó en el número 30 en el Billboard 200, y ha vendido más de 74.000 copias a partir de noviembre de 2012. Su primer sencillo del álbum "Ready or Not", se convirtió en un Top 40 éxito internacional, y alcanzó el puesto número 49 en el Billboard Hot 100. Se anunció que su segundo sencillo es "Hurricane". El video musical se estrenó el 12 de abril 2013 y fue filmado en Londres.En septiembre de 2013, se anunció que Mendler estaba trabajando en su segundo álbum. Tras varios meses de grabación, en marzo de 2014 es entrevistada en la revista Paper Magazine donde confirma que su próximo single se llamará Rome debido a sus estudios en la Universidad del Sur de California (USC), Bridgit lo uso en sus composiciones con la idea de una cultura perdida. El álbum se espera para los meses de junio o julio de 2014.

Bridgit Claire Mendler (Washington, D.C., 18 de Dezembro de 1992) é uma atriz, cantora e compositora americana. É conhecida por interpretar Teddy Duncan, protagonista da série do Disney Channel intitulada Good Luck Charlie.Bridgit fez participações como a vampira Julieta Van Heusen na série Os Feiticeiros de Waverly Place, também do Disney Channel.Em 2008, protagonizou o filme The Clique. Teve um pequeno papel no longa Alvin e os Esquilos 2 em 2009, mesmo ano em que atuou ao lado de Lindsay Lohan no filme Labor Pains.Em 2011, protagonizou o filme de sucesso Lemonade Mouth da Disney Channel. Em 2012, Mendler dublou a voz americana de Arriety no filme japonês The Secret World of Arrietty. Em 2012 Bridgit lançou seu álbum de estreia "Hello My Name Is..." que contou com uma sonoridade pop. Ele estreou na posição de numero 30 na Billboard 200, e vendeu mais de 74.000 cópias a partir de novembro de 2012. Seu primeiro single "Ready or Not" se tornou um hit internacional top 40, e chegou ao número 49 na Billboard Hot 100. Foi anunciado que seu segundo single será "Hurricane". O vídeo estreou no dia 12 de abril 2013 e foi filmado em Londres.
